snippet.title: Horizon Forbidden West - NVIDIA DLSS 3 Trailer | CES 2024
snippet.description: Check out the PC version of the Playstation post-apocalyptic epic that puts you up against giant machines and deadly storms as you race to restore order to the world. You can play it on PC early this year, along with the Burning Shores expansion.
